{"tid":1625844,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［開定先］唔好幫Vans裝修","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T16:01:49.000Z","uid":23094,"like":225,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"95707ccf137cb2c988cff5c2355513a84cd8efba","tid":1625844,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:36:20.000Z","msg":"事源：Vans舉辦設計比賽<br />\n<br />\n起因：有人以香港抗爭為主題提交設計作品，短時間內已經得到非常多票，如果勝出，Vans就會推出發售<br />\n<br />\n結果：Vans因為要政治正確而自我審查，以作品不符合參賽守則為理由，將該款參賽作品移除<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/311038659019878/posts/1280135028776898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F311038659019878%2Fposts%2F1280135028776898&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KB0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=c8af135a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/311038659019878/posts/1280135028776898</a><br />\n<br />\n我知道一定會有人會話要幫佢裝修<br />\n我想手足決定裝唔裝修之前諗清楚<br />\n<br />\n1）<br />\n首先佢唔係紅底<br />\n因為商業理由要保持中立，要政治正確<br />\n其實香港大部份國際企業都係一樣<br />\n如果真係要搞，你搞得幾多？<br />\n<br />\n2）<br />\n佢冇實際危害到呢場運動同手足<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅情況我認為抵制、罷買係最適合<br />\n<br />\n經過呢幾日，我相信多數前線手足都係克制<br />\n但唔可以排除有少部份手足比較激進<br />\n抱住有殺錯冇放過嘅心態<br />\n未了解清楚對方衰乜嘢就幫人裝修<br />\n<br />\n一芳就係最好例子<br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">知道自己做緊乜先好去做</span>"},{"pid":"32adcc14dc491ec12b1932a354f01b0c7f018360","tid":1625844,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04045355d8997efc4f6b1fe634182fd50014fedd","tid":1625844,"uid":124824,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:43:32.000Z","msg":"我都唔支持幫佢裝修<br />\n雖然佢真係無事先聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670b74bae4ef91b56ca13b388735301a848e2220","tid":1625844,"uid":280761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:44:32.000Z","msg":"同意 p牌推唔到"},{"pid":"c5d9d1c24