:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:48:12.000Z","msg":"處理咗其他中資機構先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:50:41.000Z","msg":"我都覺得對準中資先<br />\n下下開新戰線邊有咁多資源"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:54:54.000Z","msg":"同埋文宣力量有限<br />\n如果你集中搞一兩間店舖，我們都可以幫你解釋到優品360衰啲咩。<br />\n但如果你搞嘅店舖數量太多, 少少事就幫人裝修，我就要解釋幾十架店舖衰啲咩"},{"pid":"a02925f6dac304b73737a0d02a57fd954f0e133d","tid":1625844,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3b274d0cb6b380e57521e166a5ea7e126eb45f","tid":1625844,"uid":148253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"抵制咪算唔裝修，黑類先裝修!!!"},{"pid":"7e28342d0b5811429cc231bcfdc2750e1f4ad1bc","tid":1625844,"uid":157411,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mjtP9h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mjtP9h.jpg&h=666c0e5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1942652bdc69dcab18af0a63f4c82463d7b373b","tid":1625844,"uid":325108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df01ca53658df6804aa0795630fc91b98d55833e","tid":1625844,"uid":37713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:59:52.000Z","msg":"人地無直接傷害你<br />\n你地就唔好直接傷害人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相對武力</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相對武力</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相對武力</span><br />\n好重要<br />\n<br />\n同埋召喚神獸唔該大聲講點解要召喚<br />\n好多唔知頭唔知路以為無啦啦打人<br />\n係咁多 不完美 要改善 可接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝