\n<br />\n咁嘅情況我認為抵制、罷買係最適合<br />\n<br />\n經過呢幾日，我相信多數前線手足都係克制<br />\n但唔可以排除有少部份手足比較激進<br />\n抱住有殺錯冇放過嘅心態<br />\n未了解清楚對方衰乜嘢就幫人裝修<br />\n<br />\n一芳就係最好例子<br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">知道自己做緊乜先好去做</span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"你傻撚左呀？<br />\n叫香港人抵制？ 香港人做得最撚差就係哩方面<br />\n<br />\n轉頭比個8折你個個狗衝落去啦！<br />\n<br />\n裝修係最好方法<br />\n直接唔比買！"},{"pid":"b9e05766f9f8e6c4a14bcf13f26dec3d9bdec9d7","tid":1625844,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"2196ff24fe699722816e796ae0a77ee65d2c61dc","tid":1625844,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:10:57.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n佢唔算目標<br />\n<br />\n美心 福建360 吉野家才是邪惡根源"},{"pid":"49103fc6d5393fc356163b0ac96366be8049204f","tid":1625844,"uid":177219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:10:57.000Z","msg":"擺買"},{"pid":"555aef1aec23602ad39b3e616317cee8e2811155","tid":1625844,"uid":1124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:12:18.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n我覺得要裝修嘅係真係有害手足嘅中資<br />\nvans係國際企業<br />\n用網上文宣同擺買已足夠"},{"pid":"dce1dfc8f0a629a354004501d82c1f317433d2f6","tid":1625844,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:12:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ef49e08b24678c3fe7bb1f6ac692d23c243ecaf","tid":1625844,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"罷買已經夠"},{"pid":"00ffe51a075a07bac822a644fbc5c831b6746a91","tid":1625844,"uid":245078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"唔好裝修，最多唔買姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a519d9199908f9f33946c09dfa81a52e5dd1de67","tid":1625844,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"罷買"},{"pid":"4b17ac2d810b1efecb8a3df4f444f56898a8e4d1"